736
00:44:29,879 --> 00:44:30,600
Mari.

737
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:33,879
Aku saja.

738
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:39,520
Ayah.

739
00:44:41,600 --> 00:44:43,280
